author: StevenTheBrick
title: Mojo Jojo Strikes
review:
3/5

 

Great parts for cartoony themes such as this one. Mojo Jojo is a good figure, however the cape won't ever go down. Meh price as it should've been around $20-25 instead of $30. An ok building experience, but lacks in playability as it's just buildings mostly. Meaning the playability is just ok, being saved by the car and the window play feature.
